  "remarks": "\nAs Aide to the President and a member of the Presidential Executive Office, Andrei Aleksandrovich FURSENKO has directly supported the Presidency of the Russian Federation and the Government of Russia. FURSENKO is therefore an involved person who provides support for and promotes policies and actions which destabilise Ukraine and undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
